<plot>When this film was being made in 1938, Pearl Harbor was almost four years away. Poland had not been invaded yet. However, World War II was raging in Asia, where the Japanese perpetrated ghastly horrors upon the conquered populations. This contemporaneous Chinese film focuses upon one family's fate amidst the atrocity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?193816</url></doc>
